Usage:
    make test-srpm      Packs source from local HEAD and builds srpm
			locally. You can then rpmbuild it on your
			machine or elsewhere. The package has git
			commit SHA1 in its Release.

    make test-rpm       Packs source from local HEAD and builds both
			srpm and binary rpm locally. The package has
			git commit SHA1 in its Release.

The Makefile in package's directory should specify NAME and SPECFILE,
and then include this Makefile, via

	include .../rel-eng/Makefile

